```

---

## ğŸ”§ Development Notes
- Run migrations only if you **change models**:
  ```bash
  flask db migrate -m "description of change"
  flask db upgrade
  ```
- Delete `globeswap.db` **only if you want to reset the database**.
- Use:
  ```bash
  pip freeze > requirements.txt
  ```
  when adding new packages.

